Package com.itsradiix.discordwebhook

Class DiscordFileWebHook

java.lang.Object
com.itsradiix.discordwebhook.DiscordFileWebHook
public class DiscordFileWebHook extends Object
DiscordFileWebhook allows for easy message sending to your Servers through a webhook! This class represents a Discord Webhook Message with the ability to send Files! Make sure to read (the wiki page on our GitHub) to understand how to use this effectively. Also make sure to understand (Discord's documentation of Webhooks).
